<main>
<div id="mount"></div>
When you reach the Thames, do me a favour and take a deep, deep breath. Take in that smell — that oily fresh, hot dirty smell. The smell of the City. Stand there and imagine for me a river that’s burst its banks, that’s full and boiling and knocking against concrete and glass. Tell me when you’ve done that.


<<button "Okay, done">><<set $prevpass to $passage>><<goto "FG-15">><</button>>
