:: FG-15 {"position":"450,1200","size":"100,100"}
<<set $passage to "FG-15">><<set $nextpassage to "FG-16">><<audio ":all" stop>><<audio "FG_15" play>>
<main>
<div id="mount"></div>
Dad started this business when he came over from Singapore in 2034. There was a particularly bad winter, and the Thames Barrier collapsed that year. Look up at Millennium Bridge. That’s all been submerged in 2039. Crazy, huh? The water now goes all the way up to the steps of St Paul’s. So technically...you’re underwater right now. Okay, turn right and let’s row towards Blackfriars Bridge.

